messageBody:
Hi Sylvain,

You might also try www.omniglot.com and
www.langmaker.com. They have loads of natural and
constructed alphabets. There are others as well, just
do a search on google under different headings like
shorthand systems, conlangs, conalphas, alphabets,
writing systems, etc.

Take care,

B. J. de Berzsenyi

> might be able to help.

> good wishes,
